Exemple avec 4 variables pour un test batterie

Test  #value#<=25                       Resultat   <i class='icon jeedom-batterie0 ' span style="color: red;""style="font-size:12px;">#value#%</span>

Test  #value# > 25 && #value# <= 50     Resultat   <i class='icon jeedom-batterie1 ' span style="color: orange;""style="font-size:12px;">#value#%</span>

Test  #value# > 50 && #value# <= 75     Resultat   <i class='icon jeedom-batterie2 ' span style="color: yellow;""style="font-size:12px;">#value#%</span>

Test  #value# > 75 && #value# <= 100    Resultat   <i class='icon jeedom-batterie3 ' span style="color: blue;""style="font-size:12px;">#value#%</span>

